"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"大家好，我是yjwiil，今天测试happyland。\\n\\n官方教程链接：\\n\\n[https://medium.com/@happyland_finance/instructions-on-how-to-play-happyland-community-testnet-version-800dc0a2f9a7](https://medium.com/@happyland_finance/instructions-on-how-to-play-happyland-community-testnet-version-800dc0a2f9a7)\\n\\n### 1、切换网络到bsc测试网\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/7n-6aLxZzB51Sfz69tuyl.png?height=313&width=424)\\n\\n添加方法：\\n\\n[https://chainlist.org/](https://chainlist.org/)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/U-QGjl5ZW54NyCBHEBraF.png?height=421&width=862)\\n\\n解释说明：\\n\\n1、链接钱包\\n\\n2、搜索bsc\\n\\n3、添加到钱包（钱包点击同意批准）\\n\\n上述方法添加失败手动在metamask钱包进行添加如下内容：\\n\\n* Network Name: Binance Smart Chain Testnet.\\n* New RPC URL: <https://data-seed-prebsc-1-s1.binance.org:8545/>\\n* Chain ID: 97\\n* Symbol: BNB\\n* Block Explorer URL:[ https://testnet.bscscan.com](https://testnet.bscscan.com/)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/wNCSlAmeh3MNbFY3hnXBx.png?height=661&width=465)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/zoz6Muy1xwOnxpmzUSzRY.png?height=1250&width=875)\\n\\n添加完成后进行获取测试币\\n\\n[https://testnet.binance.org/faucet-smart/](https://testnet.binance.org/faucet-smart/)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Ap-jFOmVfAYJXMeW8IB2T.png?height=503&width=847)\\n\\n1、填自己的地址\\n\\n2、获取\\n\\n### 2、导入测试币的合约到钱包\\n\\n合约如下：\\n\\nHPL: 0x752f7a3a3efef9a917f1b71f1e54dbd025dbc043\\n\\nHPW: 0x88b6072ef0267006fd65cfe51d536b9156009e88\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/LOtNngIs37_qdo4ud2TyV.png?height=702&width=425)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/L6gpT8VeOrqGbRigPKI80.png?height=631&width=438)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/PWAmP1mnCb6kFYw85FtbS.png?height=157&width=493)\\n\\n第二个也如此操作，我就不进行演示了。\\n\\n### 3、进入happyland官网测试\\n\\n[https://app.happyland.finance/](https://app.happyland.finance/)\\n\\n选择链接钱包\\n\\n![钱包点击同意](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/KmmaoQ6Yd-LVO-EGqKmvt.png?height=854&width=1656)\\n\\n![然后进行注册账号设置密码](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/F6B8So8oWEa5jIUwf-Kmf.png?height=395&width=800)\\n\\n### 4、获取游戏测试币并测试\\n\\n![上面两个都点](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/5hyvJyirM9gvawdvn45PD.png?height=794&width=1054)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/fz5urYjuhA5k9nngC114u.png?height=558&width=1602)\\n\\n![然后再刷新网页](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/ARxC3Lsrc-n7eCHx8Bl3w.png?height=598&width=1449)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/rc_Knn9hU4ro4_pRYYtdA.png?height=743&width=1196)\\n\\n![上图两个都需，钱包批准](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/H0UxqHRi2fKmv4G54a-ST.png?height=324&width=800)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/J1Rj41971HMDBRMh-NSln.png?height=541&width=1095)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/F53CtsOsN2B-5zUogrhUk.png?height=590&width=806)\\n\\n### 5、进行游戏\\n\\n[https://testplay.happyland.finance/](https://testplay.happyland.finance/)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/XwuxwSBDndFH13SkJS4j3.png?height=624&width=1005)\\n\\nhappyland官方推特：\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/HappyLand_HPL](https://twitter.com/HappyLand_HPL)\\n\\n官方的discord：\\n\\n[https://discord.gg/yBSNBBPE](https://discord.gg/yBSNBBPE)\\n\\n我的推特：\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/yjw6o](https://twitter.com/yjw6o)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1642002821,\"title\":\"HappyLand测试\"},\"digest\":\"46k87SonRJ9mu2IlKP9895_rJHdZNnoAX7wcRjdFJc4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xF8F1e33fD68be886C9638a636a2EF716801383A4\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"LH_S_NTYOa_-gxBctf07Gk6CYicleCVRTvMngSclQdc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"t-_vLEbDX1cW_4bpjp-XNZp6RpMEcYOX5X6l8sre2Ls\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"UIjfX2hG_Gtwcm8GUkNWTvPdSYboWcUeeE1cyLhSworWIRqL5uqDz